content:
I completed my PhD program in Statistics in 2018 winter, under the supervision of Prof. Lang Wu in the Department of Statistics  at the University of British Columbia (UBC).
I finished my Master’s program in Statistics at UBC in 2013. In 2011, I received my Bachelor’s degree in Statistics from Zhejiang University of Finance and Economics in China. .
